context:
KR:
&lt;엿이나 먹어.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Screw yourself.&gt;

KR:
&lt;시협회에 암살자를 의뢰해서 슈렌느의 입을 막은 것도 당신 짓이지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;You also hired Shi Association's assassins to silence Shrenne, didn't you?&gt;

KR:
&lt;그런데 이상…&gt;
EN:
&lt;By the way, Yi Sang...&gt;

KR:
&lt;당신은 어디로 날아가고 싶었던 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Where did you want to fly?&gt;

KR:
&lt;그럼 지금은?&gt;
EN:
&lt;What about now?&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;……&gt;

KR:
&lt;물론이지.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Of course.&gt;

KR:
&lt;내 말이 들린 건가?&gt;
EN:
&lt;You heard what I said?&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;잘 지내시오?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Have you been well?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;거울을 볼 때마다 문득 인사를 하곤 하오.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Whenever I look at a mirror, I find myself greeting it.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;인사란 서로 주고받아야 자연스러운 것이라 하지만…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;It is said that a greeting is only natural when it is mutually exchanged...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;언젠가 전해질 거로 생각하기에 괜찮소.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;But I do not mind the one-sidedness, as I believe it will be conveyed someday.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;이제 나는, 정지하지 않을 테니 말이오.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;I have decided that from now on, I will no longer be stopped in place.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;모든 건 결국, 변하지 않겠지만…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Even if all will ultimately remain unchanging...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;나 역시도 이제, 변하지 않을 테니.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;I, too, shan't change, either.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;너무 걱정들 하지 마시오. 내 곁에는 새로이 벗들이 생겼소.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;You have no need to be overly concerned for me. I now have new companions by my side.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그들은 어찌 생각할지 모르겠으나… 나는 이들을 벗삼으려 하오.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Though I cannot be sure what they will think of this... I intend to consider them as such.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;그럼…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;To close off...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;끝에 부쳐.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Allow me one final remark.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;사는 내내 모두가 평안하시길.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;May you all keep company with peace throughout your lives.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;이상.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#d4e1e8&gt;Yours sincerely, Yi Sang.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;다들 먹는 것 하나만큼은 진심이네.&gt;
EN:
&lt;They sure are serious about eating.&gt;

KR:
&lt;어떻게 회식만 하면 저렇게 기분들이 좋아 보이지?&gt;
EN:
&lt;It amazes me how they can look so happy while eating out.&gt;

KR:
&lt;너는… 기척도 없었는데… 언제부터 거기 있던 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;You're... I didn't even notice you arrive... How long have you been there?&gt;

KR:
&lt;……&gt;
EN:
&lt;……&gt;

KR:
&lt;나는…&gt;
EN:
&lt;I…&gt;
